author: Joe Murphy
title: Afghanistan Map Game: Here are the results
text:
To the 35% who could place Afghanistan on an unmarked map of the world , strong work. To the other 18% who were off by fewer than 100 miles, not bad. And to the 11% who missed the mark in this week's map game by more than 1,000 miles, maybe you learned something.
